snippet.title: EP 62 - How Herbs Can Transform Your Health with Amber Valenzuela of Traditional Medicinals (part 1
snippet.description:
Source:
https://www.spreaker.com/user/11013532/ep-62-how-herbs-can-transform-your-healt

We rely on pharmaceutical remedies and pills a lot. But thousands of years ago, people used herbs to cure diseases and health conditions. We have forgotten that the flowers in your garden, the berries in the wild forest, and leaves on the trees can enhance your health and help you improve your well-being. Why don’t we just go back to our roots? Mareya interviews Amber Valenzuela on her experience of using herbs for remedies, enhancing your physical health and just tasting new flavors.
snippet.channelTitle: Mareya Ibrahim - Recipes for Your Best Life
